frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050985ec1a5c9445d63347dc787fc0a770df66f6","tid":142503,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T21:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係咪撞正件player咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但佢啲frd都話佢係好仔嚟 同埋佢又唔似係player款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁易比你睇得出就唔叫player啦<br />\n再了解下先好啲<br />\n再唔係主動問囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7d24c2b5fa7dd56abcc52a6f79acff54c2e4c7","tid":142503,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T21:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係咪撞正件player咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但佢啲frd都話佢係好仔嚟 同埋佢又唔似係player款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒撚都係咁的...試下下次出街主動拖佢手仔，睇睇咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒撚邊會主動攬頸搭膊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1536f87467dd7cf0fc02cdeb744b585da9a099fc","tid":142503,"uid":28053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T21:20:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係咪撞正件player咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但佢啲frd都話佢係好仔嚟 同埋佢又唔似係player款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒撚都係咁的...試下下次出街主動拖佢手仔，睇睇咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒撚邊會主動攬頸搭膊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n華生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁佢應該係偽毒乖乖仔設定既player, 樓主小心"},{"pid":"06672de423c2448aa98e03b814131edf60e5ede0","tid":142503,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit